# Public docs (API.md, ARCHITECTURE.md, INSTALLATION.md, ROADMAP.md, adr/)
# stay committed as normal project documentation.
docs/HANDOFF/
docs/DEVELOPMENT.md
docs/THESIS_ANALYSIS.md
docs/ARCHITECTURE_DIAGRAMS.md

